<template>
    <GChart
      type="Scatter"
      :data="ScatterChart"
      :options="chartOptions"
      ref="gChart"
    />
  </template>
  <script>
  import { GChart } from "vue-google-charts";
  export default {
    name: "geochart",
    components: {
      GChart,
    },
    data() {
      return {
        chartData: [
        ['Age', 'Weight'],
          [ 8,      12],
          [ 4,      5.5],
          [ 11,     14],
          [ 4,      5],
          [ 3,      3.5],
          [ 6.5,    7]
        ],
  
        chartOptions: {
            title: 'Age vs. Weight comparison',
          hAxis: {title: 'Age', minValue: 0, maxValue: 15},
          vAxis: {title: 'Weight', minValue: 0, maxValue: 15},
          legend: 'none'
        },
      };
    },
  };
  </script>
